            "detailed_description": "The Afterglow of Grisaia was originally released in Japan as a first-edition bonus for volume 5 of the Eden of Grisaia anime adaptation Blu-ray/DVD.<br />\r\nWe're excited to release it as a standalone product for the first time, fully localized for western fans to enjoy!<br />\r\nThe Afterglow of Grisaia takes the form of a side story to The Labyrinth of Grisaia (the second main series Grisaia game, also recently released in English!).<br />\r\nThe game is a story-driven visual novel with serious overtones.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Labyrinth of Grisaia shed some light on Kazami Yuuji's past, offering a deeper look at events stretching as far back as his birth.<br />\r\nThis story, however, concerns Yuuji's experiences with Kusakabe Asako, the CIRS agent who rescued him at a young age from a terrorist organization.<br />\r\nSecret passages of The Labyrinth of Grisaia are revealed within...<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt is recommended that you play this game only after having played The Labyrinth of Grisaia.",
